OL,3,CThousands join mums' WhatsApp group to
OL,4,Cstop children from having smartphones
OL,6,FBy Rachel Dixon, Multimedia Producer
OL,8,FWithin a fortnight, two mothers have
OL,9,Fcreated what they believe is the
OL,10,Flargest group of parents in Britain
OL,11,Fall pushing for one cause - to stop
OL,12,Fchildren growing up with smartphones.
OL,14,FResearch into British children's phone
OL,15,Fuse has shown the more they use social
OL,16,Fmedia, the higher their exposure to
OL,17,Fonline harassment, poor sleep,. The
OL,18,Fstudy by UCL and Southampton
OL,19,FUniversity professors found this was
OL,20,Fhigher in girls than boys.
