OL,3,CThousands join mums' WhatsApp group to
OL,4,Cstop children from having smartphones
OL,6,FAfter discovering these statistics,
OL,7,Ffriends Clare Fernyhough and Daisy
OL,8,FGreenwell set up a WhatsApp group
OL,9,Fcalled Smartphone Free Childhood.
OL,11,FTheir initial aim was to support each
OL,12,Fother, and anybody else trying to
OL,13,Fdelay buying their sons or daughters
OL,14,Fphones which use the internet and have
OL,15,Fsocial media.
OL,17,FBut in just 24 hours, thousands of
OL,18,Fother parents joined the group after
OL,19,Fan by Daisy about it went viral.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/9
