OL,3,CThousands join mums' WhatsApp group to
OL,4,Cstop children from having smartphones
OL,6,FThe group got so big that the pair had
OL,7,Fto advise parents to create their own
OL,8,Fregional WhatsApp groups. There is now
OL,9,Fone for every county in the UK.
OL,11,FTheir aim is to agree not to give
OL,12,Ftheir children smartphones until at
OL,13,Fleast 14 - currently in Britain 97% of
OL,14,F12-year-olds have a smartphone.
OL,16,FThey are not the only ones pushing for
OL,17,Fchange.
