OL,3,CThousands join mums' WhatsApp group to
OL,4,Cstop children from having smartphones
OL,6,FThis summer, parents of primary school
OL,7,Fage children in a small coastal town
OL,8,Fin agreed smart pads, and access to
OL,9,Fapps such as Snapchat, Instagram,
OL,10,FWhatsApp and TikTok.
OL,12,F"We've become more and more protective
OL,13,Fof children in the real world,
OL,14,Feverywhere you go is a safeguarded
OL,15,Fspace, and then we'll give kids a
OL,16,Fphone where there is no safeguarding
OL,17,Fwhatsoever on the internet.
