OL,3,CThousands join mums' WhatsApp group to
OL,4,Cstop children from having smartphones
OL,6,F"It's sort of a strange dichotomy that
OL,7,Fwe have between this very protected
OL,8,Freal world and a completely lawless,
OL,9,Fdigital world," Ms Greenwell,tells ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,FHer eldest child is eight, and as her
OL,13,Fdaughter grows closer to the age where
OL,14,Fshe could have a smartphone, Ms
OL,15,FGreenwell's concerns began to grow
OL,16,Fover what she would be able to access
OL,17,Fon the internet and her exposure to
OL,18,Fbullying online.
OL,20,FShe wants her children to spend time
OL,21,Fplaying, not looking at a screen.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/9
