OL,3,CThousands join mums' WhatsApp group to
OL,4,Cstop children from having smartphones
OL,6,FMrs Greenwell said: "I think we've
OL,7,Fbeen put in an impossible position by
OL,8,Ftech companies.
OL,10,F"You either allow your children access
OL,11,Fto something you know is damaging or
OL,12,Fyou risk alienating them from their
OL,13,Fpeers.
OL,15,F"The regulation hasn't caught with the
OL,16,Ftechnology, and it's parents and
OL,17,Fchildren that lose out.
