OL,3,CThousands join mums' WhatsApp group to
OL,4,Cstop children from having smartphones
OL,6,FBut after struggling to bring up the
OL,7,Fdivisive topic at the school gates, Ms
OL,8,FGreenwell and Ms Fernyhough decided to
OL,9,Fset up the WhatsApp group, to bring
OL,10,Flike minded parents together in a non-
OL,11,Fjudgmental setting.
OL,13,FWithin hours the group was filled to
OL,14,Fcapacity, so through their original
OL,15,Fchat, a network of groups have spawned
OL,16,Facross the country. There is one in
OL,17,Fevery county of the UK, some even have
OL,18,Fsub groups for specific schools.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
