OL,3,CThousands join mums' WhatsApp group to
OL,4,Cstop children from having smartphones
OL,6,FIn the chat there are 600 people, and
OL,7,Fthere are over 40 sub-groups for
OL,8,Fseparate schools, Ms Greenwell says.
OL,10,FSmartphone Free Childhood does
OL,11,Frecognise the need for parents to get
OL,12,Fin contact with their children, and
OL,13,Frecommends buying a "brick" phone,
OL,14,Fwhich only has text and call features.
OL,16,FWith their campaign building such
OL,17,Fmomentum, the Ms Greenwell and Ms
OL,18,FFernyhough hope to bring their cause
OL,19,Fto Parliament and lobby for a ban on
OL,20,Fyoung children having smartphones.
