OL,8,Foverwhelmed and for all.
OL,10,F"I guess one thing which has been
OL,11,Fextremely inspiring is this is
OL,12,Fmovement that has sprung up, and it's
OL,13,Fthe realisation that parental love is
OL,14,Fan awe inspiring force to be reckoned
OL,15,Fwith."
